trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"></xref> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 상속 될 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The TransformerInfoCollection class allows you to programmatically access and modify the `transformers` section of the `webParts` section of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: TransformerInfoCollection 클래스 프로그래밍 방식으로 액세스 하 고 수정할 수 있습니다는 `transformers` 의 섹션은 `webParts` 구성 파일의 섹션입니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo> objects, as part of a TransformerInfoCollection, specify custom classes that extend the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo>개체는 TransformerInfoCollection의 일부로 지정 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>클래스</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> 를 확장 하는 사용자 지정 클래스</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo>

trans-unit.source: These transformer classes act as bridges between connected Web Parts, translating data sent by a connection provider into something that the connection consumer can accept.
trans-unit.target: 이러한 변환기 클래스 연결 된 웹 파트 사이의 다리 역할을 연결 소비자를 수락할 수 있는 항목으로 연결 공급자가 전송에 데이터를 변환 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection"></xref> class.
The TransformerInfoCollection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: 사용자 코드에서 직접 사용할 TransformerInfoCollection 생성자를 사용 하는 것이 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET 구성 시스템에 의해 호출 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection.Transformers%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection> class always contains an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection> type.
Use this instance, rather than creating your own.
trans-unit.target: 직접 만드는 보다는이 인스턴스를 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Adds a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"></xref> object to the collection.
The collection must not already contain a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo> object with the same <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo.Name%2A> property value.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"></xref> object to add to the collection.
Removes all <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"></xref> objects from the collection.

This method removes all <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo> objects from the collection and inserts a `clear` element into the `transformers` collection of the `webParts` section of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 모두 제거 <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo>컬렉션에서 개체를 삽입 한 `clear` 요소에는 `transformers` 의 컬렉션은 `webParts` 구성 파일의 섹션.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo>

trans-unit.source: The Item property overwrites the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo> object if it already exists; otherwise, a new object is created and added to the collection.

This method removes a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo> object from the collection and, if the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo> object is defined in a higher-level configuration file, inserts a `remove` element into the `transformers` collection of the `webParts` section of the configuration file.
